content: Can I attend part of a zoom phone bank?  Is training only in the first 20 minutes?

Hi James! Yes, feel free to hop in anytime to make calls. If you can, try to join at the beginning of the session to go through training. That said, our VOTE team members are there to help with questions!
Great, thanks!  Is there an example script I could see? Just trying to get an idea
They tend to change based on the list we're calling. On the dialer there is a preview of that session's script. That said, don't worry if you need to ease yourself in. You can help at your pace!
